---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <main style="padding: 3rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: system-ui;">
    <h1>Quality Assurance (QA)</h1>

    <p>
      I protect delivery quality by making requirements testable, validating outcomes, and reducing rework.
    </p>

    <h2>What I focus on</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Test planning and QA coordination</li>
      <li>Acceptance criteria and definition of done</li>
      <li>UAT support and issue triage</li>
      <li>Clear bug reporting and verification</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How I work</h2>
    <p>
      I build quality into the process early, so testing isn’t a panic at the end — it’s a controlled checkpoint throughout.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
